<h2 id="installation">Installation</h2>

<p>Clone/download repo under <strong>~/.config/awesome</strong> and use widget in <strong>rc.lua</strong>:</p>

<div class="language-lua highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kd">local</span> <span class="n">github_contributions_widget</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">require</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"awesome-wm-widgets.github-contributions-widget.github-contributions-widget"</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="o">...</span>
<span class="n">s</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">mytasklist</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="c1">-- Middle widget</span>
	<span class="p">{</span> <span class="c1">-- Right widgets</span>
    	<span class="n">layout</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">wibox</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">layout</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">fixed</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">horizontal</span><span class="p">,</span>
		<span class="o">...</span>
		<span class="c1">-- default</span>
        <span class="n">github_contributions_widget</span><span class="p">({</span><span class="n">username</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s1">'&lt;your username&gt;'</span><span class="p">}),</span>
		<span class="o">...</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
